OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FReform UK's leader in Scotland has
OL,7,Freignited a race-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,8,Fover a speech promoting the
OL,9,Fintegration of South Asian communities
OL,10,Fin public life.
OL,12,FMalcolm Offord was accused of trying
OL,13,Fto "race-bait" the Scottish Labour
OL,14,Fleader after raising the controversial
OL,15,Fissue just a year after his party used
OL,16,Fthe same address to falsely claim Mr
OL,17,FSarwar "has said he will prioritise
OL,18,Fthe Pakistani community."
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@NO]yD@HOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
