FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FThe advert was produced as part of the
OL,7,FHamilton, Stonehouse and Larkhall by-
OL,8,Felection campaign before Mr Offord
OL,9,Fdefected from the Conservatives.
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV Border, Mr
OL,12,FOfford said it was "not necessarily
OL,13,Flanguage I would have used but what
OL,14,FI'm clear about is that if a speech is
OL,15,Fmade by any politician, those words
OL,16,Fcan be used and that is a legitimate
OL,17,Fexercise."
OL,26,@tD@TOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FChallenged over the fact Mr Sarwar did
OL,7,Fnot say the words in the Reform
OL,8,Fadvert, Mr Offord produced a card from
OL,9,Fhis jacket pocket of "other things
OL,10,Fthat he said in that speech."
OL,12,FMr Offord said: "So what he said in
OL,13,Fhis speech was, he said the following.
OL,14,F"He said: 'The days when South Asian
OL,15,Fcommunities get to lead political
OL,16,Fparties and get to lead countries is
OL,17,Fupon us'."
OL,26,@qD@VOUtD@QOUvD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FAsked if that was a bad thing, Mr
OL,7,FOfford added: "I'm just giving you
OL,8,Fthat for context. And the second thing
OL,9,Fhe said, which I would like to
OL,10,Fquestion him on, was: 'The days where
OL,11,FSouth Asian communities get to decide
OL,12,Fnot just which school our children go
OL,13,Fto but what they are taught in these
OL,14,Fschools is also coming'."
OL,26,@vD@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
