OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FMr Sarwar said on Tuesday: "Yet again
OL,7,Fit's Malcolm Offord and Reform
OL,8,Fattempting to race-bait me in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of an election campaign. Of
OL,10,Fcourse parents should have a say on
OL,11,Fwhat their children are taught in
OL,12,Fschools. It seems bizarre that Malcolm
OL,13,FOfford is saying that only some
OL,14,Fparents and not all parents in
OL,15,FScotland should have a say."
OL,17,FMr Offord also revealed that he has
OL,18,Ftold his candidates to stop endorsing
OL,19,Fthe far-right activist Tommy Robinson,
OL,20,Fwho he described as an "extremist".
OL,26,@|D@XOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FReform's candidate for Galloway and
OL,7,FWest Dumfries, Senga Beresford, sent a
OL,8,Fmessage to Mr Robinson on social media
OL,9,Fin July 2024 saying: "Behind you all
OL,10,Fthe way," after he posted about
OL,11,F"setting up in Trafalgar Square for
OL,12,Fthe biggest patriotic rally the UK has
OL,13,Fever seen".
OL,15,FIn the following days she sent a
OL,16,F"thumbs up" emoji to a post that said:
OL,17,F"Give me a Thumbs Up and RETWEET, If
OL,18,FYOU STAND WITH TOMMY ROBINSON".
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@IO]sD@AOUuD@JO]xD@AOUxD@KO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FShe also replied "Yes" to a post that
OL,7,Fsaid: "Do YOU agree with what Tommy
OL,8,FRobinson says! YES or NO?"
OL,10,FSeparately, in August 2024, she
OL,11,Freplied: "Me," to a post on the social
OL,12,Fmedia site X from Ashlea Simon, the
OL,13,Fdeputy leader of the far-right party
OL,14,FBritain First, which said: "In the UK
OL,15,FMuslims are demanding that sharia law
OL,16,Fis implemented. I demand that we
OL,17,Fdeport the lot of them. Who's with me?"
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@VO]oD@GOUpD@ZO]sD@JOUsD@NO]vD@
OL,26,A\OUyD@gO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FMr Offord insisted the meaning of that
OL,7,Fmessage was "ambiguous" and that Ms
OL,8,FBeresford was "referring to sharia
OL,9,Flaw" rather than the deportation of
OL,10,FBritish Muslims.
OL,12,FMr Sarwar has referenced that message
OL,13,Fand said it shows Ms Beresford "wants
OL,14,Fto deport my children", a claim that
OL,15,FReform has strenuously rejected.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@WO]pD@OOUqD@DO]uD@`OUvD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FPushed by ITV Border on the fact that
OL,7,Fthe message Ms Beresford says "deport
OL,8,Fthe lot of them", Mr Offord said: "She
OL,9,Freplied with a 'me' ` and I've
OL,10,Fquestioned her on this quite
OL,11,Fspecifically ` that this was a comment
OL,12,Fto say no to sharia law in the UK.
OL,13,FSimple as that."
OL,15,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,16,Fconsistently said that Mr Robinson,
OL,17,Fwhose real name is Stephen Yaxley-
OL,18,FLennon, is not welcome in the party.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@PO]pD@cOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
