PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FSeparately, Mr Offord said he
OL,7,Fpreviously "drank the Kool-Aid" and
OL,8,F"read the lines I was given" by the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment about the energy transition
OL,10,Fto net zero when he was a UK
OL,11,Fgovernment minister.
OL,13,FHe said he believes in climate change
OL,14,Fbut added that "science is always
OL,15,Fdisputed".
OL,17,FMr Offord said: "The world heats up
OL,18,Fand cools down. And heats up and cools
OL,19,Fdown. So I don't want to get into that
OL,20,Fargument about science."
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@_O]pD@AOUpD@\O]vD@POUwD@IO]yD@
OL,26,AQOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
