PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776856004
OL,3,CReform UK Scotland leader reignites
OL,4,Crace-row with Anas Sarwar
OL,6,FScottish Labour's deputy leader Jackie
OL,7,FBaillie accused Mr Offord of having
OL,8,F"doubled down on spreading racist,
OL,9,Fpoisonous bile and dangerous
OL,10,Fmisinformation".
OL,12,FShe said: "Anas Sarwar has dedicated
OL,13,Fhis life to public service and making
OL,14,FScotland a better place, and it is
OL,15,Fshameful that Malcolm Offord would try
OL,16,Fand justify a racist smear campaign
OL,17,Fagainst him.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@OO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
